column4: Hello, Speeedbus. Thanks for moving that powerline.
You may have seen on the forum that Moblet, G, and I have started our own pak 128 server; please let me know if you are interested in joining it
Just in case you get bored of 64 ;)
Yes, I saw. An I had a look at the map, it is really interesting. But ATM I don't have to much spare time.
Unfortunately I have to work a lot to make my living.
Yes, I wish I could get paid to play simutrans :)
But if you do ever wish to play just drop me a line and I will make sure that you get a prime spot ;)
Sounds great. Thank you very much
